net.hka.train.seats.booking.domain.csv.validator

Class IntegerGreaterThanZeroValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opencsv.bean.validators.MustMatchRegexExpression
      • net.hka.train.seats.booking.domain.csv.validator.IntegerGreaterThanZeroValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.opencsv.bean.validators.StringValidator

    public final class IntegerGreaterThanZeroValidator
extends com.opencsv.bean.validators.MustMatchRegexExpression

    Validator that validates on the integer that is provided as string using a preassigned regular expression and checks if the provided integer is matching a valid integer value format with value that is greater than Zero. Then the IntegerGreaterThanZeroValidator will invokes the super String.matches(String) method on the string to be converted using the preassigned regular expression string and if the two do not match then a CsvValidationException will be thrown.
